item.title: Earth Scape V2 source
item.dc:creator: @The_Reaper_X The Reaper X
item.description:
@The_Reaper_X wrote:

What chassy is trying to say is making a V1 and then getting all of the updates for a V2 in only 2 days must mean that you must not have put much more into it than your v1. When you release a whole new version, generally you should have a well variety of updates and new features that make it different than the previous version. Try to put more effort into V3, don’t come out with it in 2 days.

Other than that, looks pretty nice. Every source is different.
